*Level.hierarchy binary

# Unity files
*.unity binary
*.unity3d binary
*.prefab binary
*.unitypackage binary
*.masterbundle.manifest binary

# Binary files
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.dylib binary
*.so binary
*.zip binary
*.7z binary
